### .devcontainer/api-tests.http
### Test requests for Insight Hunter Workers
### Open this file and click "Send Request" above each section to test

### Authentication: Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8787/auth/register HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "securepassword123",
  "name": "Test User"
}

###

### Authentication: Login
POST http://localhost:8787/auth/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "securepassword123"
}

###

### Upload CSV (replace YOUR_TOKEN with actual token from login)
POST http://localhost:8787/api/upload HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="transactions.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

date,amount,description
2024-01-15,150.00,Office Supplies Purchase
2024-01-16,-2500.00,Payroll Payment
2024-01-17,5000.00,Client Payment Received
------FormBoundary--

###

### Get transactions
GET http://localhost:8787/api/transactions?limit=10 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
